eu.mondo.mondix.core

Interface IQueryInstanceDirect.RowInterpreter<Row>

  • Type Parameters:
    Row - the class that represents a tuple/row of the query results. Can be any POJO - clients should extract values using the provided tuple interpreter.
    Enclosing interface:
    IQueryInstanceDirect<Row>

    public static interface IQueryInstanceDirect.RowInterpreter<Row>
    An adapter object to interpret the internal row representation of a IQueryInstanceDirect.
    Author:
    Bergmann Gabor

    • Method Summary
